---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me — yukassa" description="クリエイティブデベロッパー yukassa のプロフィールと提供価値。">
  <article class="page">
    <header class="page__hero container">
      <p class="page__eyebrow">About Me</p>
      <h1>ものづくりの熱量をユーザー体験へ変換する人</h1>
      <p class="page__lead">
        プロダクトのフェーズに合わせて、調査・設計・実装を横断しながら「伝わる体験」を形にするという設定です。
        ここで紹介する内容はダミーポートフォリオ用に作られたフィクションであり、実在の人物・団体とは関係ありません。
      </p>
      <dl class="facts">
        <div>
          <dt>会社</dt>
          <dd>koreha_dummy_desuyo_company</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>職種</dt>
          <dd>Dummy Lead Frontend Engineer / DummyOps</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>拠点</dt>
          <dd>dummy_city / Remote</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>得意領域</dt>
          <dd>DesignOps, Frontend, Product Discovery</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </header>

    <section class="section container section--values">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2>大切にしていること</h2>
        <p>Generative な視点でプロダクトに関わる際の、3 つの価値観を記録しています。</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="values">
        <li>
          <article>
            <header>
              <span>01</span>
              <h3>問い直し続ける</h3>
            </header>
            <p>課題の解像度が合っているかを問い直し、チームで「なぜ」を共有する。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li>
          <article>
            <header>
              <span>02</span>
              <h3>データと感性の往復</h3>
            </header>
            <p>ユーザーの声とデータを往復しながら、仮説検証を小さく素早く回す。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li>
          <article>
            <header>
              <span>03</span>
              <h3>誰でも触れる仕組み</h3>
            </header>
            <p>誰もが編集しやすいドキュメントとデザインシステムで、改善のボトルネックを減らす。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section container section--timeline">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2>簡略的な履歴（すべてダミー）</h2>
        <p>生成的な探索を重ねてきたというフィクションのキャリアラインを、フェーズごとのムードで演出しています。</p>
      </div>
      <ol class="timeline">
        <li>
          <div class="timeline__period">2011 – 2015</div>
          <article class="timeline__body">
            <header>
              <h3>dummy大学 メディアデザイン学科</h3>
            </header>
            <p>触覚フィードバックを活用したダミー研究に取り組み、koreha_dummy_desuyo_award を受賞したという設定です。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="timeline__period">2015 – 2017</div>
          <article class="timeline__body">
            <header>
              <h3>dummy大学大学院 デザイン研究科</h3>
            </header>
            <p>XR とサービスデザインの融合をテーマにした架空の研究。dummy サービスハッカソンで特別賞を受賞したというフィクションです。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="timeline__period">2017 – 2019</div>
          <article class="timeline__body">
            <header>
              <h3>dummy_freelance_lab / Dummy Product Designer</h3>
            </header>
            <p>dummy_subscription や dummy_id_system などの案件を並行して担当し、すべてダミーの成果指標を残したという設定です。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="timeline__period">2020 – 2022</div>
          <article class="timeline__body">
            <header>
              <h3>dummy_creative_collective / Dummy Creative Developer</h3>
            </header>
            <p>dummy_portfolio と dummy_creator_ec を手掛け、Jamstack ワークショップを開催したというフィクションです。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="timeline__period">2022 – 現在</div>
          <article class="timeline__body">
            <header>
              <h3>koreha_dummy_desuyo_company / Dummy Lead Frontend Engineer</h3>
            </header>
            <p>dummy_design_system_refresh や dummy_ui_kpi_dashboard を推進したという想定で記載しています。</p>
          </article>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
  }

  .page__hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(3.4rem, 9vw, 5.4rem) clamp(1.8rem, 6vw, 3.2rem) 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page__hero::before,
  .page__hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page__hero::before {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 25%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.28), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 90% 15%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.32), transparent 70%);
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }

  .page__hero::after {
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, rgba(148, 163, 255, 0.22) 1px, transparent 0.9px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.22) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 220px 220px, 280px 280px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .page__hero > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .page__eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(229, 231, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .page__lead {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 760px;
    color: rgba(214, 218, 255, 0.82);
  }

  .facts {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    margin: 0;
  }

  .facts div {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: rgba(18, 22, 53, 0.88);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 113, 185, 0.35);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .facts div::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.22), transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .facts dt,
  .facts dd {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .facts dt {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(173, 177, 233, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .facts dd {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(232, 232, 255, 0.88);
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .section {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4.2rem) clamp(1.8rem, 6vw, 3.2rem);
  }

  .section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: clamp(0.6rem, 2vw, 1rem);
    border-radius: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(20, 26, 67, 0.92), rgba(12, 15, 44, 0.92));
    opacity: 0.92;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .section__header {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .section__header h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.4vw, 2.4rem);
  }

  .section__header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(210, 214, 251, 0.75);
  }

  .section--values::before {
    background:
      linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(20, 26, 67, 0.94), rgba(15, 18, 48, 0.92)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.18), transparent 60%);
    background-blend-mode: screen;
  }

  .values {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
  }

  .values li article {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.1rem);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 113, 185, 0.35);
    background: rgba(23, 28, 64, 0.92);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .values li article::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.15) 0.8px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 110px 110px;
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .values li header {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .values li header span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.22);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .values li h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .values li p {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(214, 218, 255, 0.78);
  }

  .section--timeline::before {
    background:
      linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(12, 18, 53, 0.95), rgba(8, 12, 36, 0.95)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16), transparent 60%);
  }

  .timeline {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.2rem;
    bottom: 0.2rem;
    left: clamp(0.6rem, 3vw, 1.2rem);
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(124, 113, 185, 0.35), rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25));
  }

  .timeline li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(120px, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 2.8fr);
    gap: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
  }

  .timeline li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.6rem;
    left: clamp(0.55rem, 3vw, 1.15rem);
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16);
  }

  .timeline__period {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(173, 177, 233, 0.75);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .timeline__body {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.1rem);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 113, 185, 0.32);
    background: rgba(21, 26, 62, 0.9);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .timeline__body::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 25%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.18), transparent 60%);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .timeline__body > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline__body h3 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline__body p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(214, 218, 255, 0.78);
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .timeline li {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .timeline__period {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page__hero {
      padding: clamp(2.8rem, 10vw, 3.6rem) clamp(1.2rem, 7vw, 1.8rem) 0;
    }

    .section {
      padding: clamp(2.4rem, 9vw, 3rem) clamp(1.2rem, 7vw, 1.8rem);
    }

    .section::before {
      inset: clamp(0.4rem, 3vw, 0.7rem);
      border-radius: clamp(1.6rem, 10vw, 3rem);
    }

    .timeline {
      padding-left: 0.4rem;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      left: clamp(0.2rem, 6vw, 0.6rem);
    }

    .timeline li {
      padding-left: clamp(1.2rem, 8vw, 1.8rem);
    }

    .timeline li::before {
      left: clamp(0.1rem, 6vw, 0.45rem);
    }
  }
</style>
